This subflow was created by the Web Services Wizard to invoke the get operation on https\://sungardasuat.service-now.com/u_change_failure.do?WSDL. Note that the inputs to this flow which correspond to web service inputs are optional inputs.  This is due to the fact that web services definitions usually incorrectly indicate that too many inputs are required, and mirroring those settings in the flow would force you to enter unused values when running the flow.
